--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 3.0.0 (2019-10-03)
C: Redesign role to support SELinux
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 2.4.0 (2019-09-17)
F: Update 'blackbox_exporter' to version '0.15.1'

* Version 2.3.0 (2019-09-12)
F: Update 'blackbox_exporter' to version '0.15.0'

* Version 2.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-03-15)
F: Update 'blackbox_exporter' to version '0.14.0'

* Version 2.0.2 (2019-02-06)
E: Minor cosmetic template improvement

* Version 2.0.1 (2019-02-05)
E: Use Jinja2 argument 'indentfirst' instead of 'first' (support older Jinja2 versions)

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-02-03)
C: Redesign 'blackbox_exporter_config' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.3.4 (2018-12-11)
E: Minor Jinja2 syntax improvements

* Version 0.3.3 (2018-12-11)
B: Correct Ansible tag
E: Minor Jinja2 syntax improvements

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-12-11)
E: Move 'blackbox_exporter-current.link' task from 'install' to 'enable'

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-12-11)
B: Add missing 'CAP_NET_RAW' capability
E: Restart application when new symlink is being created (i.e. version updates)

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-12-05)
F: Update 'blackbox_exporter' to version '0.13.0'

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-11-28)
E: Rename configuration file from 'config.yml' to 'blackbox.yml'

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-08-29)
B: Remove configuration files from install sequence (execute notify handler)

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-08-29)
F: Add option to configure 'config.yml' configuration file

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-08-28)
E: Ensure user's home directory is being removed during remove sequence

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-08-28)
F: Initial release
